Package com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.attestation

The com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.attestation package provides interfaces for configuring the Attestation Service.

Package com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.attestation Description

The com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.attestation package provides interfaces for configuring the Attestation Service. It attests the state of a remote infrastructure node.
